description.narrative: The Ministry of Health (MoH) has increased capacity to provide routine immunization services and targeted campaigns., which contributes to Immunization Services As Part Of Primary Health Care, Immunization Services As Part Of Primary Health Care (Covid). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Community Engagement, Social And Behaviour Change, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2024, more children, adolescents and mothers benefit from quality health interventions, including in emergency situations.
